Development workflow for Hermod features:
1. Consider privacy implications FIRST
2. Design UX before implementation
3. Write tests for AI behavior
4. Implement with tier checking
5. Test across all tiers
6. Validate performance (<50ms)
7. Update documentation
8. Test with real users
